profile:
Canada's Restoration Services is a leader in the restoration industry with over 12 years of experience. We specialize in mold removal, asbestos testing and removal, water damage restoration, fire and smoke damage and reconstruction.

We operate 24/7 and guarantee to be on site within 45 minutes for all emergencies. We provide same day appointments and have completed over 10,000 inspections and jobs nationwide. We work with every insurance company across Canada to help make the process quicker and easier for you and your family. We also provide free financing for all eligible customers to help ease any burdens.

We are a nationwide company and have been awarded over 13 years running  by HomeStars as Top Restoration Company. We value our customers and work hard to provide professional and reliable services. Call and speak to an expert today! We service Ontario, Quebec, and Alberta!

profile:
We are Design+Build company having all the professionals from A-Z  in our team. 
Before you do anything, give us a call as we are Design + Build company with Tarion new home builder, Structure engineer with 'PNG' license and working with some of the best Interior design and Architectural firms in Toronto. You will be saving so much money by choosing us instead of waisting your money by hiring a individual companies for each task. 

Based in Toronto, 'Fresh Home Innovations' has been a leader in residential renovations and custom home construction since 2000. From concept to completion, we take a client’s vision and make it a reality through a comprehensive process to ensure the finished product exceeds expectations. Choosing a reputable contractor is the most important decision you will make regarding your project. From plans and permits, to last little finishing details, freshhomeinnovations.com  is committed to completing your renovations and home improvements in a professional manner and to your complete satisfaction.

Our wealth of experience, skilled expertise and attention to detail enables us to offer you innovative solutions, competitive pricing and the ability to meet milestones. We appreciate how much your project means to you. That’s why we approach each project with professionalism, integrity and adaptability while maintaining open communication with you every step of the way. 
We pride ourselves in Home additions, renovations, custom home building, commercial renovations, condominium renovations and design and build projects.  Let us partner with you to create the home of your dreams.

We understand the family home is the most important investment most people will make in their lifetime, and you as our client have entrusted your investment to us. So whether it be a new architecturally designed or inspired home, or a renovation and extension of your existing home, you can be guaranteed that Fresh Home Innovations  is most definitely the qualified team for your project.
Our friendly, jovial and courteous staff receive ongoing training to ensure we can deliver this promise to you on a daily basis. 

 We have had the opportunity to transform your dreams into reality by designing rooms where you can relax and your children can safely play. We have enjoyed being a part of homeowners’ lives and strive to continue to provide our customers with the best technology on the market. We have completed literally thousands of renovations since our inception. We are a unique award winning contracting company, consulted by various media as industry experts. 
Please view our website at freshhomeinnovations.com to view images of some of our projects.  
Regardless of scope, we approach every single home renovation with a foundation of strong design aesthetics, comprehensive product options, sound project management, and a commitment to craftsmanship. 

Our projects range from building new custom homes, home additions and extensions, condominium renovations, architectural design and permit, structural engineering, commercial renovations, rear addition, second floor addition, basement underpinning, historical restoration, custom projects, general contracting, custom kitchen and bathrooms, residential renovations and finally we design and build everything. We take pride in our personalized service and our high quality workmanship. 

With a minimum 2 year Warranty, we at freshhomeinnovations.com  know how to design and build lasting results and lasting relationships with each of our highly respected clients. 
Our focus is on Custom projects such as custom Kitchen renovations, Basement Finishing and underpinning, Bathroom Renovation and Bathroom Remodeling, Home Additions, Second Story Additions, Rear Additions, Home Extensions and Rear Extensions, commercial renovations, office renovation, architectural drawings, permit and etc. We work with some of the top architects, interior designers, engineers and sub-trades in Toronto. We provide custom marble and tile install services as our marble and tile setters are highly skilled and detail oriented. We are the all inclusive General Contractor who will take care of all your design and general contracting needs.

Fresh Home Innovations is an innovative, full service design/build/ construction firm based in Toronto, specializing in residential clients across the GTA. With decades of construction management experience on a wide variety of residential projects, we offer a strong design aesthetic, invaluable insight, vast resources and craftsman that exceed client expectations.
Strong leadership and communication skills are the essential components necessary to navigate a construction project from concept to completion. Our extensive knowledge of all trade areas involved in both new construction and sophisticated renovations have proven invaluable to our company and our clients. Our recognition of the importance of scheduling, cost control, and quality control underlies and defines our successful completion of many challenging projects on time and within budget.

There’s many different reasons to work with us: to make room for a growing family, to improve layout or increase the resale value of your property! Our team of professionals offer customers design and build counselling along with skilled trades and top discounts, on top brands. 

There is no substitute for experience. Join the list of satisfied clients! In the end the quality of your project depends on who you hire. When you hire us, you do so because of our company’s reputation, our track record with past clients and our commitment to new ones. The registered DesignBar trademark provides DIY home owners a single source for their residential design and construction needs when buying or selling homes in the GTA.

Future Perfect Construction is a local skilled construction firm founded in 2000 by a select group of individuals with a high level of expertise in the trade. The firm specializes in Commercial and Residential Renovations, Home Inspections, New Home Builds and Construction Project Management. Future Perfect's primary goal of meeting customer's needs through quality workmanship has resulted in the pride, loyalty and trust that co-insides with our standard of excellence. The firm is always working with it's clients to exceed standards, adhere to budgets and manage strict timelines. 
We believe that the value of the dollar has come a long way so we provide our services and do business with the utmost professionalism. We aim to service customers from the initial phase of planning and cost estimates to the final stages of our warranty process. 
Contact us for a free "No Pressure" estimate and let us help you take the first step to completing your project. Advice is always free.

profile:
We-Haul is a full-service Junk Removal, Bin Rental & Demolition company, founded in 2007.

Need help getting rid of junk at your home, business or construction site? Get relief with quick, fair and reliable hauling services. We will give you a hand in digging through the clutter and removing unwanted junk from your property or job site. Our experienced staff accompanied by our maintained fleet and new trucks will pick up your trash at a competitive rate without compromising service. All junk is disposed of at appropriate transfer stations or donated to charities. Only a small portion of what we remove will be brought to a dump or landfill.

Whether you’re renovating or working on a new build, we’ve got you covered with scheduled bin rentals. Get peace of mind with reliable same-day bin switches (if scheduled before 10 am) so the crew can keep working.

Looking to get your renovation started? Or you just want to tear down that ugly, old garage you’ve been staring at the last few years? We do all types of demo work from interior walls and floors to tearing down old sheds and garages. If you are even thinking about getting some interior & exterior demolition work done, call us first! We will provide you with a written quote that is sure to beat any competitor. We are fully licensed and insured! Our services include a bin rental.

Our crew are fully-vetted, respectable and reliable. We will show up at your location and give you a FREE ON-SITE ESTIMATE before we start. If you like our quote, we will begin the job. All you have to do is relax and we will do all the dirty work.

Call now for your free quote (647) 444-5865

profile:
Junk, clutter or unwanted materials taking up space? Let us do the dirty work for you or you can rent a bin and do the work yourself.

***

Junk Kings junk removal services are offered to residential and commercial customers. We provide all-inclusive services to our clients from loading to transport to disposal of your junk. 

***

Our trucks have 20 cubic yard boxes, which is equivalent to 10 pick-up truck loads. The trucks are operated by a strong, professional and courteous staff that will evaluate the work and quote a price based on weight, volume and time. Upon agreement, the crew will load, haul and dispose of your rubbish at your earliest convenience.

Give us a call today!

Random Junk We Have Removed

Over the years Junk King has removed some very odd and random junk. This is a list of some of the items we have removed.

-Twenty-five boxes of 1940-1960 Life Magazines
-Old rotted camping trailer cut into pieces
-One full truck of expired potato chips
-Five broken slushy machines
-World War 2 Memorabilia
-Four truck loads worth of paper and cardboard from a 1 bedroom apartment
-Twelve sofas from one basement
-Crisp new $1 bills from the 1960’s hidden in an old coat pocket
-Two truck loads full of mannequin heads

APV Reno are experienced and highly skilled general contractors, home renovation specialists, and painters providing both residential and commercial general contracting needs in Toronto, Downtown Toronto, North York, Mississauga, Etobicoke and GTA areas in Ontario.

We are licensed home renovators & general contractors with over 20 years of successful experience in home renovations, residential & commercial general contracting, and painting. We also work with other professional construction trades across Toronto and the GTA.

APV Reno’s core business is in Design & Renovations. We specialize in home additions, basement renovations, basement finishing, kitchen renovations, bathroom renovations, and general higher-end residential construction.

Other home improvement services include both interior and exterior painting (residential, commercial, and industrial), interior and exterior renovations, as well as fulfilling the procurement process to acquire building permits in the City of Toronto and the GTA.

Our honesty, professionalism and meticulous attention to detail has granted us our success in the cutthroat general contractors and home renovations industry. This has subsequently helped our company build long-term relationships with both clients and contractors, enabling us to steadily grow over the last 20+ years. As a valued client, you can have complete confidence in our work.

Lastly, our integrity in achieving success on every contract or job regardless of how small or large the project, is the core component to our success. All in all, we strive to be a highly reputable and one of the best general contractors in Toronto.

Offering demolition and excavation services throughout out Toronto and the GTA. National Auto Parks Ltd. also offers hauling and delivery of aggregate materials as well as junk removal and transportation of equipment, goods and long haul move in/out. 

Did you know we specialize in complete asphalt repair services for commercial and residential properties. Pot hole repair, depressions, drainage repair, speed bumps, cracks and sealing and traffic line painting services. We also offer commercial snow cleaning and removal in the winter months.  We serve the Toronto and GTA areas as well as Halton, Peel, York and Durham regions. 

National Auto Parks Ltd. is a family owned and operated business with 30 years of experience serving the great and vibrant city of Toronto and the GTA. We are a grassroots Canadian born company built on hard work, positive and long lasting relations with honest, progressive and intuitive business practices. We are a multi-tool business with an appetite for projects and challenges. We specialize in serving the care and maintenance of commercial properties of all shapes and sizes. We have a dedicated asphalt and paving team that can repave, repair and rebuild all forms of asphalt with a specialized line painting team to repaint existing or create new parking lines for your commercial property. Additionally we have a highly regarded snow cleaning and snow removal team ready 24/7 during the winter months to ensure your commercial property is safe and operational at all times when the snow falls.

But enough about us... Contact us today, we'd love to hear about you!

profile:
Aura-Con is a Toronto based construction company that specializes in Demolition, Excavation, Foundation and Shoring Solutions. Our services include demolition of low-rise to mid-rise structures, site preparation and earthworks, bulk and detailed excavation for residential, commercial and industrial buildings. We specialize in variety of foundation and Shoring solutions such as Soldier Piles & Lagging, Caisson Walls, Structural Caissons, Sheet Piling, Underpinning, Tiebacks and Soil Anchors. At Aura-Con we have highly knowledgeable and experienced personnel at all levels of the company. Our extensive experience allows us to provide value engineering and high-quality service to our clients.

Aura-Con is equipped with a broad range of specialized equipment and highly skilled operators, which enables us to complete projects with optimal performance. Safety is our priority; we have a comprehensive safety program and safety training for all our employees. We ensure a safe work environment throughout all our projects. Aura-Con is uniquely positioned to provide value to its clients by combining Demolition, Shoring Solutions, and Excavation services thus increasing efficiency and productivity. Every project is completed with our clients needs at the forefront, providing communication, reliability and integrity.

profile:
We spent years listening to contractors try to convey to labourers what the clients needed. While clients were satisfied with the final product, they often had to sacrifice the dream they originally had. Sometimes, the clients would be told that the changes they wanted would cost a lot more extra than was needed.
​
One day, we realised that if we could work directly with the clients, that they would be able to tell us directly what they want to see, and we would be more flexible to provide it for them.
​
We have partnered with longstanding professionals who prize high quality service as much as high quality work. If we don't offer what you need, we can help you find someone who will. 
​
Whether you need our services for your home or your workplace, we intend to leave you showing off your new space, brimming with pride.

profile:
Respond, Remove, Rest Easy
Toronto Asbestos Removal provides safe, certified, and professional removal of Asbestos Containing Material ACM in Residential and Commercial buildings across Ontario.  Providing free estimates while providing calm explanations and guidance, is what sets Toronto Asbestos Removal apart from the rest of the industry.  Experts in Inspection, Sampling, Air Testing and Abatement are available to Home Owners and Business Owners.  Toronto Asbestos Removal provides candid and confidential advisory services to their clients.
SAFE AND PROFESSIONAL ASBESTOS REMOVAL
ASBESTOS REMOVAL
ASBESTOS TESTING
ASBESTOS AUDITS
PROFESSIONAL SERVICE
Toronto Asbestos Removal is a hazardous materials contractor with a range of abatement services including asbestos, lead, mold and PCB removal.
Toronto Asbestos Removal management team and field personnel have extensive experience in the abatement of hazardous materials from residential to commercial and institutional as well as industrial facilities.
Toronto Asbestos Removal has the appropriate insurance and W.S.I.B coverage, the ability to provide bonding as well as has an excellent track record with the Ministry of Labour and the Ministry of the Environment.
Toronto Asbestos Removal utilizes the latest abatement techniques to assure the safe and timely completion of all projects. All our employees have been trained in the latest asbestos techniques and are compliant with W.H.I.M.S.
Toronto Asbestos Removal provide the installation or removal of manufactured products containing asbestos, including products such as vinyl or acoustic tiles, gaskets, seals, packing, friction products, or asbestos cement products and more.
Please call for free consultation and estimate for any project large or small.
Toronto Asbestos Removal guarantees 100% asbestos removal. That means that after we have performed asbestos removal, the air you breathe is as clean as it can get.
Asbestos & Lead Removal: 
Asbestos is a natural mineral which was commonly used in homes, buildings and school for various uses such as insulation, ceiling tiles, plaster, vinyl floor tiles, roof patching, etc.
Today, asbestos is no longer used as extensively since prolonged exposure to it has proved to be hazardous to ones health. When the asbestos fibers are released into the air anyone breathing the air is at risk. Asbestos exposure has been linked to lung scaring and cancer. 
If you are unsure if products in your home or office contain asbestos you should have an Asbestos Certified Inspector inspect your home. If the product is protected and fibers are intact you can leave it as is. If the product has deteriorated it is essential to remove the asbestos from the premises.

profile:
Our ReStore Professional Services Team will come to your home and carefully and efficiently dismantle major household items such as, kitchen cabinetry, counter tops and appliances, bathroom fixtures and more.

We’ll also tackle whole home deconstructions, removing doors, windows, built-in shelving, etc. from your home carefully and professionally at absolutely no cost to you. Think of what you’ll save on demolition and disposal costs, not to mention the environmental impact.

You’ll receive a charitable tax receipt from Habitat ReStore for the assessed resale value of your donated items. Plus, all proceeds from ReStore donations go directly toward our Habitat home building projects. So, you can feel good that you’re supporting your community by helping Habitat build safe, decent and affordable homes for working, low-income families.
